# ===== SMTP Configuration =====
# Option A: Brevo (recommended for production — free tier: 300 emails/day)
# Get SMTP keys from https://app.brevo.com/settings/keys/smtp
# BREVO_HOST=smtp-relay.brevo.com
# BREVO_PORT=587
# BREVO_USER=your_brevo_email@example.com
# BREVO_PASS=your_brevo_smtp_key

# Option B: Generic SMTP (Gmail, Outlook, etc.)
# SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
# SMTP_PORT=587
# SMTP_USER=your_email@gmail.com
# SMTP_PASS=your_app_password

# Option C: mail-config.json (auto-generated file in project root, checked into git)
